Introducing GPT-5.4

Ody just got an upgrade with GPT-5.4, our most capable model for professional work. It outperforms prior models while being more token efficient, with notable improvements on long-running tasks, tool calling, computer use, and frontend development.

Learn more: https://odysseythink.com/index/introducing-gpt-5-4

You can always keep using GPT-5.3-Ody if you prefer.
